Hello juice cleanse from the best @saludjuice I’m kickstarting my health journey by doing a 3-day ‘The Freshman’ juice cleanse. It consists of drinking 6 juices each day with plenty of water in between. 
⚠️ I was scared the first time I juiced. Here are a few things I would like to share. 
•I actually felt full even with not eating solid food during the cleanse. 
•When I felt hungry, I ate an avocado 🥑 or a handful of almonds.
•I did get a headache on day 1 & 3 but, as soon as I drank more water, it went away. 💧 
•The cleanse helped rewire my brain & care about what I eat. 
•Sometimes we all need to help our body get rid of toxins & let out digestive system ‘rest’. 
Also my skin feels AMAZING .
